"tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"睇死司徒夾帶而家窮到奶粉錢都冇呀<br />\n如果佢唔係有bb可能都惡d既<br />\n為左2個衰仔脆低,男兒膝下的有黃金呀<br />\n冇d撚用.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6590d5426b6f8648ee04e58548f95c21bd928179","tid":44823,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"晚晚打老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0a96fbb6f6b64dcd3fecfe42dbb6f69d8809ab","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"你個bb仔岩岩出左黃金啦<br />\n仲唔去執錢啦司徒夾帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33aefa83e9236f8ee933795e230b65529aecf27f","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"消防死左都有人可憐夾錢<br />\n比車撞死都有人比送花圈<br />\n司徒夾帶你自己出錢啦.哈哈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e7a76dc2613ed2695bf9b7674c0d513b3dfdb9","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"今晚係創作界最黑暗既一day<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e039d8036ab7f8fefc0787885c85ccbe7baacac8","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"司徒夾帶生個仔都係貪錢偷野<br />\n一定要誅死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8256d4e37a33b5d9793826f5a3a7c0598baeb6","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"你呢種人只係識得錢<br />\n創意既野你識條鐵咩<br />\n而家罰你少少錢當交學校咋<br />\n以後做人醒醒定定呀話過你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a86777fdfa626a08640566081f8794f4a43213","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"為左個將來可能成為叉燒既bb咁樣脆低值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64faf966274d2ecc4d7d8778044bbd9c4da03534","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"正所謂你有你理由,理西你感受<br />\n錢就固之然收撚硬架啦<br />\n問題係下一步點樣可以鋤死佢老婆<br />\n床上鋤定係廚房鋤好d呢"},{"pid":"afaf2af3f750eeae76879f6c7b51b217e3c07f10","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"司徒夾帶既道歉片唔夠誠意<br />\n冇4k又沙沙聲<br />\n好想佢重拍一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ac65c229e74fc0f80034228c530e1ca10ebc7e","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"如果晚晚打老婆唔肯收錢<br />\n我考慮代佢收同埋處理<br />\n希望司徒夾帶你盡快準備定現金<br />\n提提你: 我可能唔收紙幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc49a825d7333f5c7e973c6c3e405dea43e9dc","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"扼殺創業定係扼殺人生<br />\n你自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb404e2b710217eca04355e51d33b7d36d6b2cb1","tid":44823,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"大佬你係本人黎嫁喎<br />\n定我真心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37e2c43a0d2b6b238e9ffc3af62ef2c0339c7a9","tid":44823,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大佬你係本人黎嫁喎<br />\n定我真心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想知可以去問本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1727e2cd8582e2221abbc25ddf9979c15e29f17","tid":44823,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"你做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}